                    <li><strong>Transfer:</strong> Send tokens to other users</li>
                    <li><strong>Monitor:</strong> Track your portfolio performance</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background-color: #fff3cd; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <h4>ðŸ’¡ Pro Tips:</h4>
