                    <li>Keep track of market trends</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;">
                <strong>Need help?</strong> Contact our support team at support@ditokens.com or visit our help center.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Â© 2024 DiTokens CRM. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #bdc3c7;">
                This email confirms your token purchase. Please keep it for your records.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
